{"tid":1018392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼警嚴刑逼供 用2米巨蛇纏疑犯","createTime":"2019-02-12T08:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T16:36:37.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5053b3ca323e05a7b0b9dc15c91d94255761f2b1","tid":1018392,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:17:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Wi8gXxRnHMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWi8gXxRnHMk&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=e08a58a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Wi8gXxRnHMk</a><br />\n<br />\n印尼互聯網廣傳一則影片，警方用蛇拷問一名盜竊犯，讓疑犯嚇得不停尖叫求饒，而一旁的警員則是哈哈大笑，印尼警方承認此事並致歉。<br />\n<br />\n影片長達1分20秒，該名疑犯被鎖上手扣坐在地上，一條至少2米長的深棕色巨蛇直接纏繞在他的頸部和腰部，其中一名警員甚至將蛇的頭部抓向該男子的臉，一邊逼問他偷了多少次手機，嚇得他不停扭頭大叫。影片中一個男聲要求男子不能閉上眼睛，還一度威脅要把蛇放進男子嘴裡和褲襠裡。<br />\n<br />\n印尼東部邊境、新幾內亞的「巴布亞省」（Papua）警方對此拷問方式致歉，表示「調查人員這樣審訊並不專業」。他說，警員為了逼供，自己想出這種方法。但表明這條蛇無毒，警員也沒動用肢體暴力威迫男子。<br />\n<br />\n人權律師柯嫚（Veronica Koman）10日轉發這則令人沮喪的影片，批評審訊根本為酷刑，已違反警方政策及法律。柯嫚說，這次事件並非首例，波根（Sam Pokon）為西巴布亞省全國委員會成員，該委員會主張從印尼獨立，波根於一月份被捕後遭到毆打，隨後被關在一間有蛇的牢房內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/930472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F930472&d=DoGI4G7aG2aFCjNgNSWIuvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=7e53e2a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F930472&h=d12b0b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/930472</a>"},{"pid":"5286e0e9d1f3aa5bb03fdf694418cef1a001b427","tid":1018392,"uid":198362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"無撚用"},{"pid":"65fd4c74de6f198caa24c904cf7edd3954b64103","tid":1018392,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:22:12.000Z","msg":"咁又點<br />\n又唔係毒蛇  又無勒緊佢<br />\n軟皮蛇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228bc5e40c041a14ee9fd7eb3c3720f639745705","tid":1018392,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"還一度威脅要把蛇放進男子嘴裡和褲襠裡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用條蛇含撚 用埋條蛇脷玩馬眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1793b205764f4a5caf084222d453ed09840d8355","tid":1018392,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"蛇身粗度直徑2米就話有威嚇作用姐，圖中幼到"},{"pid":"53d18edb6c04634e664f60bb2680328347bd2eb1","tid":1018392,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228bc5e40c041a14ee9fd7eb3c3720f639745705","tid":1018392,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"還一度威脅要把蛇放進男子嘴裡和褲襠裡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用條蛇含撚 用埋條蛇脷玩馬眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"諗起豹子頭俾包大人撚鳩"},{"pid":"df076af37f23f2c61c63681b19eaf91b658f78a2","tid":1018392,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac7ecb800add5393a945af1299d3f850eda9